OL,3,CAngry Ginge targeted for calling out
OL,4,C'racist' fan at World Cup game
OL,6,FYoutuber Angry Ginge has revealed he
OL,7,Fwas targeted with a torrent of online
OL,8,Fabuse after speaking out against
OL,9,Falleged racism at an England World Cup
OL,10,Ffixture.
OL,12,FThe content creator attempted to have
OL,13,Fa spectator ejected from the Boston
OL,14,Fstadium during the Three Lions' draw
OL,15,Fagainst Ghana, accusing the man of
OL,16,Fmaking "incredibly racist comments"
OL,17,Fdirected at the Ghanian national team.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
