OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782647292
OL,3,CAngry Ginge targeted for calling out
OL,4,C'racist' fan at World Cup game
OL,6,FAngry Ginge, whose real name is Morgan
OL,7,FBurtwistle, says he reported the
OL,8,Fincident immediately, providing
OL,9,Fseveral witnesses, but stadium
OL,10,Fsecurity allegedly failed to take any
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,FThe influencer expressed his
OL,14,Ffrustration with the American stewards
OL,15,Fon-site, who reportedly informed him
OL,16,Fthat the spectator would only be
OL,17,Fremoved if he was "caught making
OL,18,Fanother racist remark".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782647292
OL,3,CAngry Ginge targeted for calling out
OL,4,C'racist' fan at World Cup game
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old, from Salford, Greater
OL,7,FManchester, described the the venue's
OL,8,Falleged protocol as "ridiculous" in a
OL,9,Fvlog uploaded to YouTube after the
OL,10,Fmatch.
OL,12,FHe said: "To be told someone has to
OL,13,Fracially abuse players a second time
OL,14,Fbefore they can be kicked out is just
OL,15,Funbelievable."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
