PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782647292
OL,3,CAngry Ginge targeted for calling out
OL,4,C'racist' fan at World Cup game
OL,6,FBut his decision to intervene and
OL,7,Fhighlight the incident has sparked
OL,8,Fsome backlash, with the influencer
OL,9,Fsharing screenshots of the abuse he
OL,10,Fhas since received online for standing
OL,11,Fup to racism.
OL,13,FThe post was captioned with: "Standing
OL,14,Fup to racism gets you this? What a
OL,15,Fworld we live in."
OL,17,FThe incident has raised fresh
OL,18,Fquestions surrounding fan behaviour
OL,19,Fand the robustness of anti-racism
OL,20,Fprotocols at major international
OL,21,Ftournaments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
